Useful [[building elements]] in [[passive solar design]], giving [[shade]] in summer, and allowing the sun to enter in winter.

The effect is similar to [[eaves]], except awnings can be added after the building has been built, and be adjusted, and can be lowered, well below the top of the [[window]] itself.

